Almost Famous;;92;;89;;R;;Set in 1973, it chronicles the funny and often poignant coming of age of 15-year-old William, an unabashed music fan who is inspired by the seminal bands of the time. When his love of music lands him an assignment from Rolling Stone magazine to interview the up-and-coming band Stillwater -- fronted by lead guitar Russell Hammond and lead singer Jeff Bebe William embarks on an eye-opening journey with the band's tour, despite the objections of his protective mother.;;Drama,Comedy,Music;;Cameron Crowe;;2000;;Billy Crudup,Frances McDormand,Kate Hudson,Jason Lee,Patrick Fugit,Anna Paquin,Fairuza Balk,Noah Taylor,Zooey Deschanel,John Fedevich,Bijou Phillips,Philip Seymour Hoffman,Eion Bailey,Terry Chen;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/almost_famous